OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly dry
OL,6,Fthis evening across England and Wales,
OL,7,Fbut frequent and locally heavy showers
OL,8,Ffor Northern Ireland and Scotland.
OL,9,FThese spreading to most areas
OL,10,Fovernight. Turning rather chilly under
OL,11,Fthe clearest skies.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FSunny spells and showers.
OL,14,FShowers most frequent in the north
OL,15,Fwhere they could be heavy and thundery
OL,16,Fat times. A cool feeling day for the
OL,17,Ftime of year.
